<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Bohuslav und Johann von Schwanberg, Pfleger zu Tachau</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Dankward Birkner, Diener der Stadt, wegen Waren Nürnberger Kaufleute an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_438" id="218v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_438_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Bohuſlaw <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Swannemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_438_r1l2">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / VVir <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> / Dankwarten Birkner </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_438_r1l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell <expan>cʒürede<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_438_r1l4">habe vnd kauffmanſchaft wegen / Vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc ut in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_438_r1l5">Johan <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu <expan>Swannemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_438" id="218v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Bohuslaw, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                                <expan>Swannemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> Dankwarten Birkner,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        edell <expan>czü rede<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> habe und kauffmanschaft wegen und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Johan, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czu
                            <expan>Swannemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
